title: This Bert Show Member Is In Big Trouble If She Doesn't Break Her Bad Habit!
description:
This week on Moe’s podcast In the Moement, He, Keity, and Just Romeo are trying to break bad habits and we are supposed to hold each other accountable. Now, in the event that someone falls short of their habit-breaking, each person was assigned a punishment. 
You’d never guess what Keity’s punishment is! It’s so terrible, Moe feels bad that he actually has to do it.
